<h1> Peter Schiff Speaks With "Occupy" Protestors </h1>

<body>
<p> Peter Schiff is the CEO and Chief Global Strategist of Euro Pacific Capital, Inc., a broker-dealer based in Connecticut. Mr Schiff has offices around the United States, and happened to be in his Manhattan office during the "Occupy Wall Street" movement. He decided to go down and attempt to create a dialogue with protestors, hoping to change their minds on who they should be protesting.</p> 

